# Holiday Home Booking Project Rules
- Environment: Static Frontend (GitHub Pages) + Backend (Google Apps Script).
- Cost Constraint: $0 (No paid tiers).
- Styling: Tailwind CSS (Modern, clean "Airbnb" aesthetic).
- Calendar Library: FullCalendar.io (Resource Timeline view).
- Data Flow: Frontend -> Fetch API -> Google Apps Script Web App -> Google Sheets.
- Formatting: Use ISO 8601 for all date handling to avoid timezone issues.
- Security: Implement a simple "Family Access Code" stored in a constant.